# Healthcare Claims Processing – UML Sequence Diagram

sequenceDiagram
    participant Provider
    participant ClaimsSystem as Claims Processing System
    participant EligibilitySystem
    participant PricingEngine
    participant PaymentSystem

    Provider->>ClaimsSystem: Submit Claim
    ClaimsSystem->>EligibilitySystem: Verify Member Eligibility
    EligibilitySystem-->>ClaimsSystem: Eligibility Status

    alt Eligible
        ClaimsSystem->>PricingEngine: Apply Pricing Rules
        PricingEngine-->>ClaimsSystem: Priced Claim
        ClaimsSystem->>PaymentSystem: Generate Payment
        PaymentSystem-->>ClaimsSystem: Payment Confirmation
        ClaimsSystem-->>Provider: Claim Approved & Paid
    else Not Eligible
        ClaimsSystem-->>Provider: Claim Denied (Eligibility)
    end
